        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl mb-6">Meet Eko</h1>

        <h2 class="text-accent text-xl mb-6">
          Photographer • Expedition Leader • Local Expert
        </h2>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          For more than three decades, I have explored Indonesia's extraordinary
          landscapes, cultures, and wildlife with a camera in hand.
        </p>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          What began as a passion for photography eventually became something
          much larger — a lifelong journey of discovering the stories,
          traditions, and people that make Indonesia one of the most diverse and
          inspiring countries on Earth.
        </p>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-2xl
        mb-6">
          My belief is simple:
        </p>

        <blockquote class="text-primary
        text-1xl
        mb-6
        p-3">
          <p class="italic">
            The best photographs are not created by visiting beautiful places.<br
            />
            They are created through meaningful experiences, genuine human connections,
            and moments that cannot be staged.
          </p>
        </blockquote>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          That belief became the foundation of <strong>Through Indonesia</strong
          >.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-6" />

        <h2 class="text-primary
        text-3xl
        mb-6">
          Why Travel With Me?
        </h2>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          Over the years, I have led private photography journeys, workshops,
          and expeditions across Indonesia, developing a deep understanding of
          both the destinations and the logistics required to create seamless
          and rewarding travel experiences.
        </p>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          Whether tracking orangutans through the rainforests of Borneo,
          documenting traditional ceremonies in remote villages, or
          photographing sunrise above volcanic landscapes, my goal remains the
          same:
        </p>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          To help travelers experience Indonesia in a way that is authentic,
          inspiring, and unforgettable.
        </p>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          Unlike traditional tours, every expedition is designed around:
        </p>

        <ul
          class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6
        p-3
        list-disc"
        >
          <li>Photography opportunities</li>
          <li>Cultural immersion</li>
          <li>Local connections</li>
          <li>Small group experiences</li>
          <li>Access to locations beyond typical tourist routes</li>
        </ul>

        <hr class="my-6" />

        <h2 class="text-primary
        text-3xl
        mb-6">
          Professional Highlights
        </h2>

        <ul
          class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6
        p-3
        list-disc"
        >
          <li>Photographer since 1991</li>
          <li>More than 30 years of experience photographing Indonesia</li>
          <li>National Photography Competition Judge</li>
          <li>Workshop Speaker and Photography Mentor</li>
          <li>Bronze Medal Recipient — Salon Foto Indonesia 2024</li>
          <li>Contributor to Agromedia Magazine since 2008</li>
          <li>
            Former Chief Curator and Judge — Gallery Photography Indonesia
            (2011–2013)
          </li>
          <li>
            Expedition leader across Bali, Java, Borneo, Sumba, Lombok,
            Sulawesi, and Eastern Indonesia
          </li>
        </ul>

        <hr class="my-6" />

        <h2 class="text-primary
        text-3xl
        mb-6">
          Through Indonesia
        </h2>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          Through Indonesia was created from a simple vision:
        </p>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          To offer photography journeys that go beyond landscapes and iconic
          locations.
        </p>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          We believe that Indonesia is best experienced through its people,
          traditions, wildlife, and stories.
        </p>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          Our expeditions combine:
        </p>

        <ul
          class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6
        p-3
        list-disc"
        >
          <li>World-class photography opportunities</li>
          <li>Authentic cultural experiences</li>
          <li>Local knowledge and logistics expertise</li>
          <li>Small groups and personal mentoring</li>
          <li>Responsible and respectful travel</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        my-6">
          The result is not simply a workshop or a tour.
        </p>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          It is an experience designed to help photographers and travelers
          connect more deeply with Indonesia — and return home with images and
          memories that could not have been created anywhere else.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-6" />

        <h2 class="text-primary
        text-3xl
        mb-6">
          What You Can Expect
        </h2>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          When you join a Through Indonesia expedition, you can expect:
        </p>

        <ul
          class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6
        p-3
        list-[check]"
        >
          <li>Small group experiences</li>
          <li>Personal photography mentoring</li>
          <li>Drone mentoring for beginner pilots</li>
          <li>Local cultural access and authentic encounters</li>
          <li>Carefully planned logistics and timing</li>
          <li>Flexibility for weather and photographic opportunities</li>
          <li>A strong focus on storytelling and visual creativity</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          For beginner drone pilots, I personally provide mentoring and
          supervision until participants are comfortable flying independently
          and safely in the field.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-6" />

        <h2 class="text-primary
        text-3xl
        mb-6">My Promise</h2>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          My responsibility extends beyond photography instruction.
        </p>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          As your expedition leader, my goal is to ensure that every participant
          feels supported, inspired, and fully immersed in the experience.
        </p>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          Because the journeys we remember most are rarely about the places
          themselves.
        </p>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          They are about the people we meet, the stories we witness, and the
          moments we never expected to find.
        </p>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          I look forward to sharing Indonesia with you.
        </p>

        <p class="text-primary
        text-xl
        mb-6">
          <strong>— Eko Sumartopo</strong><br />
          Founder, Through Indonesia
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- <div class="w-full ml-auto">
        <img
          src={profileImage}
          alt="Eko Sumartopo"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
      </div> -->
    </div>
  </Container>
</MainLayout>
